Attributions
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This project's skill-system structure and its brainstorm -> plan -> build
workflow are inspired by and adapted from Superpowers by Jesse Vincent
(https://github.com/obra/superpowers), which is licensed under the MIT License.
Superpowers' patterns — intent-named skills, `Use when ...` trigger
descriptions, a SessionStart orientation hook, and a brainstorming-before-
implementation flow — were adapted (not copied verbatim) for CloudGrid's
product. Some short trigger phrasings (e.g. "before any creative work, explore
the user's intent, requirements, and design before implementation") echo
Superpowers' wording.

